#: ../../source/news/releases/0.x/announcing-0.4/index.rst:4
msgid ""
"This release has only got a few weeks’ worth of changes, as we stabilize "
"our monthly release process. In addition to the usual pile of bug fixes "
"and performance improvements, this release includes the items below."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/0.x/announcing-0.4/index.rst:8
msgid "{{< relnote >}}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/0.x/announcing-0.4/index.rst:11
msgid "General"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/0.x/announcing-0.4/index.rst:13
msgid ""
"**Cloud Foundry**. Added minimum Pilot support for the `Cloud Foundry "
"<https://www.cloudfoundry.org>`_ platform, making it possible for Pilot "
"to discover CF services and service instances."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/0.x/announcing-0.4/index.rst:17
msgid ""
"**Circonus**. Mixer now includes an adapter for the `Circonus "
"<https://www.circonus.com>`_ analytics and monitoring platform."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/0.x/announcing-0.4/index.rst:21
msgid "**Pilot Metrics**. Pilot now collects metrics for diagnostics."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/0.x/announcing-0.4/index.rst:23
msgid "**Helm Charts**. We now provide Helm charts to install Istio."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/0.x/announcing-0.4/index.rst:25
msgid ""
"**Enhanced Attribute Expressions**. Mixer’s expression language gained a "
"few new functions to make it easier to write policy rules. `Learn more "
"</docs/reference/config/policy-and-telemetry/expression-language/>`_"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/0.x/announcing-0.4/index.rst:30
msgid ""
"If you’re into the nitty-gritty details, you can see our more detailed "
"low-level release notes `here "
